# Implementation Tasks: Byte Bridges Enterprise Website

**Feature**: 001-byte-bridges-enterprise
**Branch**: `001-byte-bridges-enterprise`
**Date**: 2025-11-07

## Overview

This document provides the complete, executable task breakdown for implementing the Byte Bridges enterprise consultancy website. Tasks are organized by user story to enable independent implementation and incremental delivery.

## User Story Mapping

| Story | Priority | Requirements | Description |
|-------|----------|--------------|-------------|
| US1 | P1 | FR-001, FR-002, FR-004 | Homepage with services, industries, testimonials |
| US2 | P1 | FR-003 | Case studies library with filtering |
| US3 | P1 | FR-005, FR-006 | Multi-step contact form with email |
| US4 | P2 | FR-007, FR-010 | Blog/knowledge hub with admin management |
| US5 | P2 | FR-009 | Admin authentication |
| US6 | P2 | FR-011 | Case study admin management |
| US7 | P2 | FR-008 | Global search functionality |
| US8 | P3 | FR-012 | Technology stack showcase |
| US9 | P3 | FR-013, FR-014, FR-015, FR-016 | Responsive design, analytics, accessibility, compliance |

## MVP Scope

**Minimum Viable Product** (first deployment): US1 + US3 + US5
- Homepage showcasing services and industries
- Contact form for lead generation
- Basic admin authentication

**Phase 2** additions: US2 + US4 + US6
- Case studies library
- Blog with content management

**Phase 3** enhancements: US7 + US8 + US9
- Search functionality
- Technology showcase
- Performance & compliance optimization

