## Phase 4: User Story 3 - Contact Form (P1)

**Story**: As a visitor, I want to submit a contact form with my project details

**Test Criteria**:
- Multi-step form (3 steps) works correctly
- Form validation shows clear error messages
- Submission sends email to admin
- User receives confirmation email
- GDPR consent is required and tracked
- Rate limiting prevents spam (max 3 submissions/hour per IP)

### Implementation Tasks

- [ ] T046 [US3] Create multi-step contact form component at src/components/forms/ContactForm.tsx with React Hook Form
- [ ] T047 [US3] Create form step 1: BasicInfo component at src/components/forms/ContactFormStep1.tsx
- [ ] T048 [US3] Create form step 2: ProjectDetails component at src/components/forms/ContactFormStep2.tsx
- [ ] T049 [US3] Create form step 3: Message component at src/components/forms/ContactFormStep3.tsx
- [ ] T050 [US3] Create contact page at src/app/contact/page.tsx
- [ ] T051 [US3] Create POST /api/contact route at src/app/api/contact/route.ts
- [ ] T052 [US3] Implement contact form validation with Zod in API route
- [ ] T053 [US3] Implement rate limiting check (IP-based, 3/hour) in contact API
- [ ] T054 [US3] Implement database insertion for contact_submissions table
- [ ] T055 [US3] Implement email notification to admin using Nodemailer
- [ ] T056 [US3] Implement confirmation email to user
- [ ] T057 [US3] Add Google Analytics event tracking for form submission
- [ ] T058 [US3] Create success confirmation component at src/components/ContactSuccess.tsx
- [ ] T059 [US3] Test contact form end-to-end with Playwright at tests/e2e/contact.spec.ts

