## Phase 11: User Story 9 - Polish & Compliance (P3)

**Story**: As a user, I expect the site to be fast, accessible, compliant, and work on all devices

**Test Criteria**:
- Lighthouse score >90 on all core pages
- WCAG 2.1 Level AA compliance verified
- Google Analytics tracking works
- Cookie consent banner appears and functions
- Data retention policy is enforced (2-year retention for contacts)
- Responsive design works on mobile, tablet, desktop
- Core Web Vitals meet targets (LCP <2.5s, FID <100ms, CLS <0.1)

