▼              ▼              ▼              ▼
US1: Homepage  US3: Contact  US5: Auth      US8: Tech Stack
(Independent)  (Independent) (Blocks US4,6) (Independent)
               │
               │ Requires US5
               ▼
       ┌───────┴────────┐
       │                │
       ▼                ▼
    US4: Blog      US6: Case Study Admin
    (Independent)  (Independent)
       │
       │ Can leverage blog/case data
       ▼
